rrent Heads of State of G20}}\n{{Current G20 Leaders}}\n{{BRICS}}\n{{Current APEC Leaders}}\n{{Current SCO Leaders}}\n}}\n|titlestyle=background: #CC0000; color:gold;}}\n{{Portal bar|China|Biography|Politics}}\n{{Subject bar|commons=y|n=y|n-search=Category:Xi Jinping|wikt=y|wikt-search=Category:en:Xi Jinping|q=y|s=y|s-search=Author:Xi Jinping|d=y|d-search=Q15031}}{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Xi, Jinping}}\n[[Category:Xi Jinping| ]]\n[[Category:Xi Jinping family| ]]\n[[Category:1953 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century Chinese politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Chinese politicians]]\n[[Category:Chinese nationalists]]\n[[Category:Philosophers from Beijing]]\n[[Category:Communist rulers]]\n[[Category:Communist Party of China politicians from Beijing]]\n[[Category:General Secretaries and Chairmen of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:Governors of Fujian]]\n[[Category:Governors of Zhejiang]]\n[[Category:Members of the 17th Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:Members of the 18th Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:Members of the 19th Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:People's Republic of China politicians from Beijing]]\n[[Category:Presidents of the People's Republic of China]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Nishan-e-Pakistan]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Olympic Order]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Abdulaziz al Saud]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Jos\u00e9 Marti]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of St. Andrew]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of the Liberator]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of the Republic (Serbia)]]\n[[Category:Chinese male writers]]\n[[Category:Sent-down youths]]\n[[Category:Tsinghua University alumni]]\n[[Category:Vice Presidents of the People's Republic of China]]\n[[Category:People's Republic of China philosophers]]\n[[Category:Victims of the Cultural 